Description: Provides statistical and visualization tools for the
    analysis of demographic indicators, and spatio-temporal behavior and
    characterization of outbreaks of vector-borne diseases (VBDs) in
    Colombia. It implements travel times estimated from [Bravo-Vega C.,
    Santos-Vega M., & Cordovez J.M.
    (2022)]<doi:10.1371/journal.pntd.0011117>, and the endemic
    chanel method [Bortman, M.
    (1999)]<https://iris.paho.org/handle/10665.2/8562>.
